            <title><![CDATA[Trails in the Sky 1st Chapter character trailer – Kloe Rinz]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/07/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter-character-trailer-kloe-rinz</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter-character-trailer-%E2%80%93-kloe-rinz.1241388/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>A kind-hearted girl devoted to helping the orphanage.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><a title="Companies > Nihon Falcom [740 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/nihon-falcom">Falcom</a> has released the fifth character trailer for <em><a title="Games > Trails in the Sky 1st Chapter [14 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter">Trails in the Sky 1st Chapter</a></em>, introducing Kloe Rinz. <span id="more-978285"></span></p><p>Here is her official description:</p><blockquote><p>A kind-hearted girl devoted to helping the orphanage.</p><p>A student at the prestigious Jenis Royal Academy in the Ruan region.</p><p>On her days off, she helps out at a nearby orphanage, where her kind and gentle nature has earned her the trust of the children and the headmistress.</p><p>Although they can’t speak the same language, she shares a close bond with the white falcon Sieg.</p><!-- AD: content -->
        <p>She becomes acquainted with Estelle and Joshua while visting a nearby village on business related to the orphanage.</p></blockquote><p><em>Trails in the Sky 1st Chapter</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [9,884 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [17,334 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [23,650 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3375780/Trails_in_the_Sky_1st_Chapter/" target="_blank">Steam</a> on September 19 worldwide. Read more about the game <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/03/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter-details-main-characters-voice-cast">here</a>, <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/05/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter-details-rolent-characters-and-places-battle-system">here</a>, <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/06/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter-details-bose-characters-and-places-location-trailers">here</a>, <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/06/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter-details-tactical-orbments">here</a>, and <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/07/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter-details-ruan-characters-and-places-trailer">here</a>.</p><p>Watch the trailer below.</p><h2><span>Character Trailer: Kloe Rinz</span></h2><p><strong>English</strong></p><p><iframe title="Kloe Character Trailer - Trails in the Sky 1st Chapter" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-SZlv7jsk4g?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Japanese</strong></p><p><iframe title="【クローゼ】キャラクタームービー #空の軌跡the1st" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/PFdKSLHMYJ0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Korean</strong></p><p><iframe title="【클로제】 캐릭터 무비 #하늘의궤적 #the1st" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3zuB9_vZ_0Q?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Traditional Chinese</strong></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【克蘿賽】 角色影片 #空之軌跡the1st" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gL6ATBe0mik?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Simplified Chinese</strong></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【克萝赛】 角色视频 #空之轨迹the1st" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Zlu8f1sK__w?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/07/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter-character-trailer-kloe-rinz]]></content:encoded>
