        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[Atelier Ryza Secret Trilogy Deluxe Pack announced for PS5, Switch 2, PS4, Switch, and PC]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/07/atelier-ryza-secret-trilogy-deluxe-pack-announced-for-ps5-switch-2-ps4-switch-and-pc</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/atelier-ryza-secret-trilogy-deluxe-pack-announced-for-ps5-switch-2-ps4-switch-and-pc.1241256/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > Koei Tecmo Games [3,076 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/koei-tecmo-games">Koei Tecmo</a> and developer <a title="Companies > Gust [809 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/koei-tecmo-games/gust">Gust</a> have announced <em><a title="Games > Atelier Ryza Secret Trilogy Deluxe Pack" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/atelier-ryza-secret-trilogy-deluxe-pack">Atelier Ryza Secret Trilogy Deluxe Pack</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [9,884 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [234 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,156 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [17,334 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [23,650 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> (Steam). It will launch in 2025. <span id="more-978287"></span></p><p>The collection includes <em><a title="Series > Atelier [57 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/series/atelier">Atelier</a> Ryza: Ever Darkness &amp; the Secret Hideout DX</em>, <em>Atelier Ryza 2: Lost Legends &amp; the Secret Fairy DX</em>, and <em><a title="Games > Atelier Ryza 3: Alchemist of the End &amp; the Secret Key [17 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/atelier-ryza-3-alchemist-of-the-end-the-secret-key">Atelier Ryza 3: Alchemist of the End &amp; the Secret Key</a> DX</em>, as well as exclusive content such as new playable characters and new story elements for all three titles.</p><p>A special live stream dedicated to <em>Atelier Ryza Secret Trilogy Deluxe Pack</em> is planned for <a href="https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?iso=20250804T1200" target="_blank">August 4 at 5:00 a.m. PT / 8:00 a.m. ET</a>, which will reveal further information and footage.</p><p>Watch the announcement teaser trailer below.</p><h2><span>Announce Teaser Trailer</span></h2><p><strong>English</strong></p><!-- AD: content -->
        <p><iframe title="Atelier Ryza Secret Trilogy Deluxe pack - Teaser Trailer" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Xl1f4aYkfSU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Japanese</strong></p><p><iframe title="『ライザのアトリエ ～秘密トリロジー～ DX』ティザートレーラー" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/MsgnndhQA34?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/07/atelier-ryza-secret-trilogy-deluxe-pack-announced-for-ps5-switch-2-ps4-switch-and-pc]]></content:encoded>
